GIT, Docker, Jenkins, terraform, packer, java and maven installation
=====================================================================
Playground: https://killercoda.com/login > signup with your google > click on playground > then, click on ubuntu

1)TIPS> All the software is having some version, majorly you can read like:
      <Major-version>.<Minor-version>.<fix-pack>

2)Mostly software-name --version This is command to check software version

3) Many time it will ask for Y/n, we need to select y from keyboard and press enter.

1)GIT
=====
Installation: apt install git
Uninstallation: apt-get remove git
Version check: git --version

2)Java
======
apt install openjdk-17-jre-headless
apt remove openjdk-17-jre-headless
java --version

ubuntu $ java --version
openjdk 11.0.19 2023-04-18
OpenJDK Runtime Environment (build 11.0.19+7-post-Ubuntu-0ubuntu120.04.1)
OpenJDK 64-Bit Server VM (build 11.0.19+7-post-Ubuntu-0ubuntu120.04.1, mixed mode, sharing)

ubuntu $ java --version
openjdk 17.0.7 2023-04-18
OpenJDK Runtime Environment (build 17.0.7+7-Ubuntu-0ubuntu120.04)
OpenJDK 64-Bit Server VM (build 17.0.7+7-Ubuntu-0ubuntu120.04, mixed mode, sharing)

Docker
======
intall: apt install docker.io
uninstall: apt remove docker.io
version check: docker --version

Exacize: Take a unix[server] box and install docker, GIT and Java

Terraform and packer
====================
>>> owner of terraform and packer is Heshicorp

https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/downloads

wget -O- https://apt.releases.hashicorp.com/gpg | sudo gpg --dearmor -o /usr/share/keyrings/hashicorp-archive-keyring.gpg
echo "deb [signed-by=/usr/share/keyrings/hashicorp-archive-keyring.gpg] https://apt.releases.hashicorp.com $(lsb_release -cs) main" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/hashicorp.list
sudo apt update && sudo apt install terraform


wget -O- https://apt.releases.hashicorp.com/gpg | sudo gpg --dearmor -o /usr/share/keyrings/hashicorp-archive-keyring.gpg

echo "deb [signed-by=/usr/share/keyrings/hashicorp-archive-keyring.gpg] https://apt.releases.hashicorp.com $(lsb_release -cs) main" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/hashicorp.list

sudo apt update && sudo apt install terraform

sudo apt update && sudo apt install packer

Exacize 2: Install terraform and packer
copy: control + C
Insert: shift + insert
